<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Ticket #{{ticketId}} Status Update</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 style="color: #333;">Ticket Status Update</h1>
    <h2 style="color: #007cba;">Ticket #{{ticketId}}: {{ticketTitle}}</h2>
    <p>The status of your ticket has been updated to: <strong style="color: #007cba;">{{newStatus}}</strong></p>
    <p>You can view the full details in the JasaWeb Client Portal.</p>
    <a href="{{ticketLink}}" style="background-color: #007cba; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 10px 0;">
      View Ticket
    </a>
    <br>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The JasaWeb Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>